<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٣٧٥ - أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3148">‌الْعَبَّاسُ بْنُ الْوَلِيدِ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6832">‌أَبِي</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4434">‌وَعُقْبَةُ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3375">‌الْأَوْزَاعِيِّ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4385">‌عَطَاءٌ </a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٠٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2">‌مَنْ سَمِعَ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">‌ابْنَ عُمَرَ </a>يَقُولُ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ: <span class="c2">«مَنْ صَامَ الْأَبَدَ فَلَا صَامَ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>